        textEn: 'Gabriel Axel was the first Danish director to win an Oscar, for Babette\'s Feast (1987). Bille August won both an Oscar and the Palme d\'Or for Pelle the Conqueror (1987). Susanne Bier won both an Oscar and a Golden Globe for In a Better World (2010).',
