        textEn: 'Mads Mikkelsen (b. 1965) received the award for Best Actor at Cannes 2012 for The Hunt. He has also appeared in the James Bond film Casino Royale (2006). Sofie Grabol (b. 1968) became known for the TV series The Killing (2007-12), which became very popular internationally.',
